product.name: GINOWY- Floor Mats & Cargo Liner for Jeep Wagoneer 2022-2025,8 Passenger, TPE All Weather Car Mats, Custom Fit Trunk Mat Waterproof Floor Liners Accessories Black
product.description:
GINOWY will provide considerate service, if you have any questions during use, please feel free to ask. We will definitely do our best to solve your problem. This is our commitment and the principle that the GINOWY brand has always adhered to.
Car floor mats may slightly curl due to packaging methods, and laying them flat for a day will slowly restore their original state. In addition, due to the possibility of slight odor from vacuum packaging, please do not worry. After drying, it will slowly evaporate.
GINOWY car floor mats fit perfectly like a glove. They use 3D scanning technology to collect original car data and fit perfectly into the car floor. A complete set of molds are customized for each model to ensure a perfect fit with the vehicle.
The buckles that match the original car will firmly secure the car floor mats and prevent the floor mats from sliding, making them strong and stable, ensuring your comfort during driving.
GINOWY car floor mats are made of TPE material, which has the advantages of stronger toughness, durability, elasticity, wear resistance, and scratch resistance. And its unique texture design can effectively prevent slipping.
GINOWY car floor mats do not hindering the accelerator & brakes, do not obstructing the car seat rails, designed to provide you with a comfortable driving environment.
The raised edges can effectively collect falling soil, debris, snacks, prevent garbage from overflowing, etc., and protect your car floor from liquids and dirt.
Car floor mats are made of waterproof TPE rubber material, which makes them easy to clean. Just wipe the surface with a cloth or rinse with a water gun.
product.bullet_points:
• 【Custom Fit】: For Jeep Wagoneer 2022 2023 2024 2025 (Only for 8 Passenger Model / 2nd row with bench Seats)
• 【3D Laser & No Trimming】 floor mats for Jeep Wagoneer 2025 applied 3D Laser tech innovation , which combines the advantages of traditional car mats and modern car mats, making it both the wear-resistant and durable. Based on 3D high-precision laser scanner, this kind of TPE car mats are precisely matched to the original car 1:1, just like a glove, truly both practical and stylish.
• 【Soft & Durable TPE Rubber】 Floor Mats for Jeep Wagoneer 2024 TPE material is extremely malleable and durable, non-slip and anti-friction, soft and waterproof.
• 【Easy to Install & Clean】 just place the Wagoneer car mats on the car floor and tighten the snaps. Easy to care, you can wipe with a wet cloth or rinse with water and dry.When they get dirty, just pull them out, spray them off, and set them in the Sun to dry
• 【All Weather/Season】 GINOWY's Wagoneer all weather car floor mats can be used in all seasons, especially in cold winters or hot summers. They will not deform or break and are extremely durable.
